<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV111">
<l>vaituniṉṉai vallavāpa ḻittavarkkum māṟilpōr</l>
<l>ceytuniṉṉai ceṟṟatīyiṉ ventavarkkum vantuṉṉai</l>
<l>eytalāku meṉparāta lālemmāya nāyiṉēṉ</l>
<l>ceytakuṟṟam naṟṟamāka vēkoḷñāla nātaṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>They say that it is possible for those who revile You [as much as] possible</l>
<l>by insulting You and for those who burned in the fire of Your anger,</l>
<l>waging matchless wars, to come and reach You.</l>
<l>Therefore, our wonderful [Lord]!</l>
<l>Take the offences that I, a dog, committed as [acts of] goodness,</l>
<l rend="indent">O Lord of the universe!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
